Michelle Stafford https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michelle_Stafford 0 Michelle Stafford (born September 14, 1965) is an American actress, screenwriter and producer. She is perhaps best known for her role as Phyllis Summers on the CBS daytime soap opera The Young and the Restless, for which she has won two Daytime Emmy Awards. In 2013, Stafford created and starred in her own comedy web series, The Stafford Project. She currently stars as Nina Reeves on the ABC daytime soap opera General Hospital.
